[Character 20 Codes\Enable Skill Slots Modifier (01-20)]
author=Code Master, Pyriel
description=It will activate the amount of slots needed for how many skills you want to have. It's fairly advanced to use this, so the less experienced cheaters should probably just modify the skills they have already to what they want by using the Skill Modifier only codes and not this code.
patch=1,EE,1028A59E,extended,00000000

